snippet.title: AntiChamber - SPOILERS - Impossible Paths - Hmm and WTF
snippet.description:
Playlist: http://goo.gl/vVD8O
The Yellow (hmm) and Red (WTF) rooms in AntiChamber, the impossible paths room.
You'll need the yellow and red guns respectively.

WTF: 0:00
Hmm: 0:44
For hmm, you can totally use them same technique as WTF if you have the red gun.
After WTF is Hitting a Wall: http://youtu.be/Pez81vW0xMU
